 Arsenal will host holders Manchester City in the Carabao Cup quarter-finals, with Manchester United heading to Everton.
Tottenham face an away trip to Championship side Stoke City, while Brentford will host Newcastle in the club’s first ever League Cup quarter-final match, reports Sky Sports.
All of the last-eight fixtures will be played on December 22/23, 2020.
Quarter-final draw
Stoke vs Tottenham
Brentford vs Newcastle
Arsenal vs Man City
